{"tid":2061213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根本個紅官同納粹嘅 Roland Freisler 冇分別","createTime":"2020-06-12T08:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T04:27:11.000Z","uid":7542,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4f28ee635b5db7989af14d007e3d7708f35b07","tid":2061213,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>破口大罵、侮辱人格、充滿偏見、無理指控⋯⋯ </strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度有一條<strong>真實嘅歷史片</strong><br />\n睇吓<strong>納粹</strong>嘅政治法庭<br />\n惡名昭彰嘅法官 Roland Freisler<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kAfQrQW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkAfQrQW.jpg&h=40697971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以聽吓佢係<strong>點樣鬧人</strong>嘅：@6:50<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBufF8VPWDZg&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=d719b606\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BufF8VPWDZg</a><br />\n<br />\n鬧佢人渣、鬧佢垃圾、然後一味擦納粹黨鞋<br />\n發癲地大聲質疑被告嘅品格⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有分別咩？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f6c94079bfb1b1dfab32c42f6c85af7207fb6700","tid":2061213,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec457d03e5ee9051edae68e2706af2c1a67a06d","tid":2061213,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94e28c3c57f26ee2f79d1416cb55500cb8957a1","tid":2061213,"uid":7542,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"有好多人覺得將香港同埋納粹比較係太激進<br />\n<br />\n甚至怕咁樣做係等於比壓力司法機構<br />\n<br />\n根本歷史上邊就有太多事件係可以做一個對照<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得法庭真係一個應該進行主觀批判嘅地方咩？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我我要講清楚<br />\n<br />\n無人想比壓力任何法官甚至嘗試左右佢判案<br />\n<br />\n但係作為法官嘅 integrity 同 manner 好重要<br />\n<br />\n呢個已經唔係講緊佢判案嘅質素<br />\n<br />\n監察法官嘅表現係每個人嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n所以你唔需要懼怕亦都唔應該恐懼<br />\n<br />\n廣傳條片比所有人自己作一個判斷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0509f85b8cc5bff6f72c2a6facf85868fd26fe49","tid":2061213,"uid":13375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:31:35.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"fbbe5d0d9d87405438c1fea1d32c8381f04c42e1","tid":2061213,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:32:10.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"7c4b0eb3944ae532fe41f05405f82519e96649f6","tid":2061213,"uid":265839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"黑官只係黑警隻狗"},{"pid":"855f44515a7598351a22ae9f8db7d2b7c9ff33da","tid":2061213,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4456ae0e3ed4ab18549b29482c006feb64fc47cc","tid":2061213,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75fe54776b67a20a3beba185479122332475193","tid":2061213,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:40:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"944d5678c6ccaf9af1ebb49113812de3fe16c6ca","tid":2061213,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:42:58.000Z","m